Patch Set 1:

we can also reproduce the issue with simple java test client provided AAI url is accessible:

RestEndpointConfig endpointConfig = new RestEndpointConfig();
endpointConfig.setBasicAuthPassword("AAI");
endpointConfig.setBasicAuthUserName("AAI");
endpointConfig.setRestAuthenticationMode(RestAuthenticationMode.SSL_BASIC);
ActiveInventoryAdapter adapter = new ActiveInventoryAdapter(null, null, endpointConfig);
adapter.queryActiveInventory("https://localhost:8443/aai/v13/search/nodes-query?search-node-type=pnf&filter=hostname:EXISTS", "application/json");

Without fix we get error like this:
18:58:06.453 [main] INFO AAIRESTClient - AC0004I|AC0004I request at url = https://localhost:8443/aai/v13/search/nodes-query?search-node-type=pnf&filter=hostname:EXISTS resulted in http response: 403 Forbidden|

With the fix we get successful message :
18:57:23.882 [main] INFO AAIRESTClient - AC0004I|AC0004I request at url = https://localhost:8443/aai/v13/search/nodes-query?search-node-type=pnf&filter=hostname:EXISTS resulted in http response: 200 OK|

